Paper: hep-th/9702183

Date: 1997-02-26

Title: On the free field realization of $WBC_n$ algebras

Comments: 9 pages, Latex, reference added, to appear in Phys. Let. B

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B402 (1997) 81-86

Defining the $WBC_n$ algebras as the commutant of certain screening charges aspecial form for the classical generators is obtained which does not changeunder quantisation. This enables us to give explicitly the first few generatorsin a compact form for arbitrary $WBC_n$ algebras.